These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
3 different pets are kept: pony, fish, frog
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, rugby, surfing
1. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the frog is the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Pet   | pony | fish | frog   |
| Sport      | biathlon    | rugby  | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, tea
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, hiking, rock-climbing
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | fanta     | tea      |
| Hobby   | hiking | camping | rock-climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  lawyer, analyst, musician
There 3 different types of food: plum, radish, raspberry
1. the analyst is on the right of the person eating radish##1
2. the musician is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the lawyer is on the left of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Job   | lawyer | musician  | analyst       |
| Food       | plum     | radish | raspberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  social-worker, photographer, paramedic
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, woodworking
1. the photographer is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the social-worker is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Job    | paramedic    | photographer     | social-worker |
| Hobby   | woodworking | card-games | puzzles     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, havana, siglo
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, trike, van
1. the person driving the trike is the siglo-smoker##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
3. the siglo-smoker is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the cain-smoker is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Cigar         | havana | cain     | siglo |
| Transport   | van        | airplane | trike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, daisy, balloon-flower
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, motorbike, train
1. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Flower        | balloon-flower | amaryllis      | daisy  |
| Transport   | boat       | motorbike | train |

