.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, trance
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, orchid, daffodil
1. the fan of trance is the person who growslily##1
2. the person who growslily is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |
| Music-Genre   | classical | trance   | punk  |
| Flower   | daffodil    | lily | orchid |

