.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-12::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, reggae, salsa
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, november, march
1. the fan of metal is in the middle##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa    | metal     | reggae   |
| Birthday   | november | february | march |

