The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, journalist, social-worker
1. the journalist is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person watching western movies is in the middle##1
3. the dressmaker is on the right of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |       1       |     2      |     3      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller     | western   | mystery     |
| Job    | social-worker | journalist | dressmaker |

