.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, iced-tea, juice
House: ranch-style, modern, art-deco
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the art-deco house is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the modern house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Beverage      | 7up  | juice | iced-tea  |
| House   | modern | art-deco   | ranch-style |

