.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, pepper, spinach
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, almond-milk
1. the person drinking water is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person eating cherry##1
3. the person eating pepper is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Food    | spinach | cherry       | pepper  |
| Beverage   | almond-milk  | water | iced-tea |

 